4.00	The_Truce_Hurts	The Truce Hurts	The Truce Hurts is a 1948 one-reel animated cartoon and is the 35th Tom and Jerry short. The title is a pun on 'the truth hurts". It was produced in Technicolor and released to theatres on July 17, 1948 by Metro-Goldwyn Mayer.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/5a/Trucehurtstitle.jpg/220px-Trucehurtstitle.jpg
